Class Summary

ConditionTag This data class converts Cursor objects returned from the database into ConditionTag objects.
ConditionUser This data class converts Cursor objects returned from the database into ConditionUser objects.
DatabaseEntry This abstract class represents rows in the application database.
DatabaseManager This is the database controller for the MoleFinder application, the database contains three tables.
MoleFinderModel This model class interacts with the DatabaseManager to provide usable objects when querying the database.
